<%# Phase 7.5 §11b — banner row.
    Renders the cached banner image when `banner_url` is present.
    Per locked decision (LOCK 3) the row is HIDDEN entirely when
    `banner_url` is nil — no colored placeholder, no empty block.
    Once ChannelSync populates `banner_url` (Phase 8) the row appears.
%>
<% if channel.banner_url.present? %>
  <div class="channel-banner" style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
    <%= image_tag channel.banner_url,
                  alt: "channel banner",
                  style: "display: block; width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 200px; object-fit: cover; border: 1px solid #ddd;" %>
  </div>
<% end %>
